OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry, bright morning,
OL,6,Fperhaps the odd light shower. Turning
OL,7,Fovercast through the afternoon as rain
OL,8,Farrives from the west, heavy for a
OL,9,Ftime. Occasionally strong, blustery
OL,10,Fwinds developing through the afternoon
OL,11,Fin the west.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy, damp evening with
OL,14,Fheavy rain clearing eastwards.
OL,15,FRemaining rather cloudy through the
OL,16,Frest of the night with light and
OL,17,Fpatchy rain in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
