OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright day with sunny
OL,6,Fspells and scattered showers, the best
OL,7,Fof the sunnier spells in the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Occasional strong and
OL,9,Fblustery winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable, often cloudy and windy few
OL,13,Fdays with spells of rain, occasionally
OL,14,Fheavy and persistent in the west. Best
OL,15,Fof the drier, brighter spells around
OL,16,Fthe Moray Firth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
